{"id":62093,"title":"[Treating aplasia through home hospital care].","abstract":"Home care is developing for patients suffering from haematological-oncological pathologies. The nurses and the whole team of the home hospitalisation department of the Léon-Bérard Centre in Lyon are prepared to deal with aplasia. Depending on its seriousness, the patient may be hospitalised or treated at home.","date":"2014-03-14","categories":"Hemic and Lymphatic Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24624717","annotations":[{"name":"Hospital","weight":0.384306,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hospital"},{"name":"Home care","weight":0.20333,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Home_care"},{"name":"Nurse","weight":0.107046,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nurse"},{"name":"Patient","weight":0.101782,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patient"},{"name":"Suffering","weight":0.0370044,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Suffering"},{"name":"Pathology","weight":0.0355959,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pathology"},{"name":"Departments of France","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Departments_of_France"},{"name":"Lyon","weight":0.0287296,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lyon"},{"name":"Centre (French region)","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Centre_(French_region)"},{"name":"Hospitalization","weight":0.0162839,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hospitalization"},{"name":"Home","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Home"},{"name":"Aplasia","weight":0.0127068,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aplasia"}]}
